ShadOck (SHADing blOCKs)

Requires Arnold 4.2.12.0 or above

Dependencies
============

   ArnoldAnimCurve    v2.0.10
   ArnoldNoiseShaders v1.1.11
   SeExprArnold       v2.0.0 (optional LLVM backend support)
   ArnoldStateShaders v1.1.8
   ArnoldUserDataRamp v1.1.4

How to
======

- Build SeExprArnold with llvm backend
  
  > scons seexpr-use-llvm=1 with-llvm=<llvm_prefix>

  SeExpr requires LLVM 3.>=8 with RTTI enabled.

  LLVM build is not integrated with SeExprArnold yet but should be pretty easy to do:

  > git clone git://github.com/gatgui/llvm.git
  > cd llvm
  > git checkout release_39
  > scons llvm-enable-rtti=1 

  Then wait for at least a good 10 minutes on a fast 4 core machine (hint: call scons with the -j <n> option with <n> set to twice the number of cores)
  
  The path to resulting 'release' sub folder is what you shoud set for <llvm_prefix>.

  LLVM backend is disabled by default.
